them about why certain things happened the way that they do.

31
00:01:22,840 --> 00:01:24,890
Discovering hacks and errors involves

32
00:01:24,890 --> 00:01:28,250
a little bit more user interaction than just watching people out in the wild.

33
00:01:28,250 --> 00:01:30,410
So, how about we do that if we're doing something

34
